# DD-4: Release Coordination
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All production releases

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Release Coordination: Scheduling and managing dependencies for production releases.

ENFORCE: All dependent services must be confirmed available; release must be scheduled with approval before execution.
PROHIBIT: Uncoordinated releases; ignoring dependency checks.
ON VIOLATION: Halt release → notify orchestrator and DevOps manager.
